EARLY CHILDHOOD EDUCATION AND SERVICES 1.1 1.2 1.3 1.4 1.5 Standard 1: Explain, demonstrate, and integrate processes of thinking, communication, leadership, and management in order to apply family and consumer sciences knowledge and skills.
